      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DODGY BEAR (8) goes very well this course and distance starting six times for four wins and two minors. Recorded a 6 length win (27.58) in a Grade 5/6 last time at this track. Looks a leading chance on best. NOT ATROCIOUS (1) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 6th at this track following on from a second place finish (27.79) there the start prior. Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Has performed well from this box with a win and five minor placings to her name from eight starts. Has the ability to give this a shake. ASTON BRADLEY (2) found traffic in the run and collided, missing the frame when a 4 length fifth (28.13) at this track in a Grade 4/5. May be worth another try. SUNSET DIABLO (5) was in the money again last time and not beaten far when third (27.91) at this track in a Grade 5.",
